BEGIN_PGML

For a given 2-D flow field it is known that the x-directional velocity is [`u = [$a]x - 3`] [`m/s`]. It is also known that y-velocity [`v = 0`] when [`y = 2`] [`m`]. At the point [`([$x],[$y])`] in the flow field, what is the y-velocity, [`v([$x],[$y])`]?



[`v=`][____] [`m/s`]

END_PGML

